{"tid":1369761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"726 元朗口號","createTime":"2019-07-26T19:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T01:25:58.000Z","uid":242734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12dbd27914206612954f87b92ca0964c44ffc8f1","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:03:10.000Z","msg":"每次遊行成日聽到香港人加油悶悶地，香港人咁有幽默感緊係要整啲新口號，況且附近咁多居民，叫口號可加強文宣<br />\n<br />\n由於有人屈示威者拆墳，依個口號必須講<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\">君堯call 黑打巿民，仲未回水被拆墳</span><br />\r\n<br />\n要講下遊行目的<br />\r\n2. 保護元朗居民，反對警黑合作<br />\r\n<br />\n搞下笑用<br />\r\n3. 提防瘋狗症，白狗亂咬人<br />\n<br />\n沙田個單未完，元朗yoho 又封商場交通指示<br />\n4. 新鴻基,sell Hong Kong <br />\r\n<br />\n\r<br />\n因為元朗太多人投建制派，都要叫下口號講建制派有幾衰，另外港鐵開閘白衫打人都要整個口號，暫時未諗到，依家拋磗引玉，大家幫幫手諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa13b61fefd05b2961a27537247cf77177b238b","tid":1369761,"uid":280209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:04:07.000Z","msg":"鄉黑牛屎佬 吊你死老母"},{"pid":"9cecd3c21897696da0bf85bbc2fa24f7f8e28d2a","tid":1369761,"uid":112860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:05:13.000Z","msg":"元朗獨立！"},{"pid":"c677a5d9bd4b3327a55a862f0c7d6afa0d0bc9f3","tid":1369761,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:05:35.000Z","msg":"君堯call 黑打巿民，仲未回水<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抵</strong></span>拆墳<br />\n<br />\n順口啲"},{"pid":"3b88ac6596e31837625989b1bd1189884f9da293","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c677a5d9bd4b3327a55a862f0c7d6afa0d0bc9f3","tid":1369761,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:05:35.000Z","msg":"君堯call 黑打巿民，仲未回水<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抵</strong></span>拆墳<br />\n<br />\n順口啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又好似係"},{"pid":"ea97aa406a04647eef2d7fe68d108cb40646e8df","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"君堯call 黑打巿民，仲未回水抵拆墳"},{"pid":"44fe2146b3535ae54221c0f8d4913972292037d4","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:14:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9085b2cec77f22ddaca1e323223b1198d162720c","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e2c36ce8c01e59b5e8db9d3bf60fb73edfd84fab","tid":1369761,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}